name: Freddy Panda - KuD-059
description:
He was a criminal who run away from prison. After running away, in the middle of the night he's been found by the family of his victims. He was ganged up, locked up, disfigured by knife and killed by burning his body in boiler room.

His spirit wants revenge. He want to kill them with the exact method they killed him. He start hunting in the middle of the night, searching for them and entering their dreams. He torturing them like what they did to him in their dream and made it real when they woke up. He's doing it until they crazy and kill them with his claw which made of knife.
